javax.constraints

Interface ConstrainedVariable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Var, VarBool, VarReal, VarSet, VarString
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractConstrainedVariable, AbstractVar, AbstractVarReal, BasicVarSet, BasicVarString

    public interface ConstrainedVariable
    This is a base interface for all constrained variable. It defines variable names, a Problem to which the variable belongs to, an associated business object, etc.
